<div class="interest-box">
<h4>üîÑ 4. Flexible Thinking</h4>
<p>Adapting to changing circumstances, considering multiple perspectives, and switching between different approaches when needed.</p>
</div>
<div class="interest-box">
<h4>‚öñÔ∏è 5. Critical Thinking</h4>
<p>Evaluating information objectively, questioning assumptions, identifying biases, and making reasoned judgments.</p>
</div>
<div class="interest-box">
<h4>üé® 6. Divergent Thinking</h4>
<p>Exploring multiple possible solutions, brainstorming diverse ideas, and embracing variety in thought processes.</p>
</div>
<div class="interest-box">
<h4>üéØ 7. Convergent Thinking</h4>
<p>Narrowing down options to find the single best solution, focusing on efficiency and optimization.</p>
</div>
<div class="interest-box">
<h4>üîÆ 8. Strategic Thinking</h4>
