<p><strong>Hypothesis:</strong> HRV Biofeedback group will demonstrate significantly higher task performance (Relative Expected Value) compared to Active Control</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Predicted Effect:</strong> Cohen's d ‚â• 0.50</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Controls:</strong> Baseline HRV, respiratory parameters, age, sex</p>
</div>
<div class="highlight-box" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
<h4 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">H2: Physiological Mediation</h4>
<p><strong>Hypothesis:</strong> Group effect on performance will be mediated by magnitude of HRV increase (ŒîlogRMSSD)</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Analysis:</strong> Causal mediation with 5,000 bootstrap iterations</p>
</div>
