      <p><strong>Author:</strong> Lotfifar, A. M.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Full Title:</strong> The E.M.E.R.G.E+ Framework: A Theoretical Model for Meaning Emergence Through Dual Entropy Dynamics</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Date:</strong> December 2025</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Type:</strong> Theoretical research article + computational simulations (no empirical participant data; n = 0)</p>
