      <li><strong>Interventions:</strong> filter abstinence, media‚Äëliteracy/self‚Äëcompassion training, and graded exposure to unfiltered self‚Äëpresentation, with explicit effect‚Äësize targets in hypotheses.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="detail-section">
    <h3>Methodological roadmap &amp; ethics</h3>
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p style="margin:0 0 10px 0;">
